<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SkiPool - Home</title>
    <style>
        body { /* general body style */
            font-family: "Markazi Text", serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        header { /* main header style */
            background-color: #1e3d58;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 { /* main head */
            font-family: "Goldman", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 36px;
        }
        header img { /* head image */
            width: 60%;
            display: block;
            margin: 10px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        section.introduction { /* section introduction */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        section.introduction h2 { /* introduction header */
            font-family: "Goldman", sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #1e3d58;
        }
        section.introduction p { /* introduction paragraph*/
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        section.features { /* features section */
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        section.features .feature { /* individual feature boxes */
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 30%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            min-width: 280px;
        }
        section.features .feature h3 { /* feature headings */
            font-family: "Goldman", sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1e3d58;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        section.features .feature p { /* feature paragraph */
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .cta { /* call to action */
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #1e3d58;
            padding: 40px;
            color: white;
        }
        .cta h2 { /* call to action header */
            font-family: "Goldman", sans-serif;
            font-size: 32px;
        }
        .cta a { /* sign up button */
            font-family: "Goldman", sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #f39c12;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .cta a:hover { /* hover effect for button */
            background-color: #e67e22;
        }
        p { /* paragraph style */
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body> 
    <header>
        <h1>SkiPool</h1>
        <p>Your Ride-Sharing Community for Winter Adventures</p>
        <img src="../../resources/img/mountains.jpg" alt="Mountains">
    </header>

    <section class="introduction">
        <h2>Welcome to SkiPool!</h2>
        <p>SkiPool connects skiers and snowboarders, making winter trips more affordable, eco-friendly, and fun. Whether you're looking for a ride to the slopes or offering one, SkiPool helps you save money while building a positive, inclusive community. Join us today and share the ride!</p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Save on Travel Costs</h3>
            <p>Share the cost of gas, parking, and tolls with others to make skiing more affordable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Reduce Your Environmental Impact</h3>
            <p>Carpooling to the slopes reduces the carbon footprint of your trip, helping preserve the mountains for future generations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Build a Positive Community</h3>
            <p>Meet fellow outdoor enthusiasts, rate and review your fellow riders, and ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for everyone.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="cta">
        <h2>Ready to hit the slopes?</h2>
        <p>Join SkiPool today to connect with other skiers and snowboarders, and start sharing the ride!</p>
        <a href="/register">Sign Up Now</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>